{"tid":60140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國廠商在車展大怒要求撤下台灣國旗，台灣廠商一句話完美K.O.","createTime":"2016-12-30T08:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T23:10:14.000Z","uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39afc5925b6549ebeb3c10daaa45c0c1e016ba96","tid":60140,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:13:17.000Z","msg":"在國際的圈子內，台灣時常受到中國的打壓，就連代表國家的旗幟也無法出現，不過在這次美國舉辦的汽車電子零配件展（SEMA）中，卻有台灣廠商直接在攤位後面掛上大大的台灣國旗，惹得其他中國廠商非常不滿，頻頻向SEMA的主辦單位抗議，不過台灣的廠商只回了一句話，就叫他們氣得臉紅脖子粗，卻說不出反駁的話！<br />\n<br />\n▼今年在拉斯維加斯舉行的汽車零配件展中，其中一個參展的台灣廠商直接用了一整面國旗當作裝飾，引發許多中國的廠商大怒，不但到攤位上要台灣廠商撤掉，還決定要向主辦單位抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img-default.newsrep.net/i.img?u=http%3a%2f%2fnewsrepmedia.blob.core.windows.net%2fimage%2f2015-11%2f51747018_00_d-600x450_f-0_c-300x225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg-default.newsrep.net%2Fi.img%3Fu%3Dhttp%253a%252f%252fnewsrepmedia.blob.core.windows.net%252fimage%252f2015-11%252f51747018_00_d-600x450_f-0_c-300x225.jpg&h=50b41e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼旗幟上面書寫了「台灣精神，世界第一」，中國廠商看了就喊說：「台灣不是個國家，憑什麼用國旗當成攤位的背景！」要求他們要撤掉這面旗幟，但廠商聽了只是淡淡地回應說：「你都知道這叫國旗了，那我們就是國家！走開吧，別在這兒惹人嫌！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img-default.newsrep.net/i.img?u=http%3a%2f%2fnewsrepmedia.blob.core.windows.net%2fimage%2f2015-11%2f51747018_01_d-648x486_f-0_c-324x243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg-default.newsrep.net%2Fi.img%3Fu%3Dhttp%253a%252f%252fnewsrepmedia.blob.core.windows.net%252fimage%252f2015-11%252f51747018_01_d-648x486_f-0_c-324x243.jpg&h=aa4ef192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼貼出照片的網友說，非常感謝主辦單位都不理這些抗議，一直到展覽結束時，這個台灣的旗幟都還存在。他在最後幾天跟SEMA主席吃飯時，再度提起了這個抗議的事，沒想到主席喝了口啤酒說：「那個國家攤位的人跟蒼蠅一樣嗡嗡叫吵死了，我們吃飯就別提這種會讓人食慾不振的事了！」<br />\nImage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img-default.newsrep.net/i.img?u=http%3a%2f%2fnewsrepmedia.blob.core.windows.net%2fimage%2f2015-11%2f51747018_02_d-1024x768_f-0_c-512x384.jpg&amp;w=843&amp;h=768\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg-default.newsrep.net%2Fi.img%3Fu%3Dhttp%253a%252f%252fnewsrepmedia.blob.core.windows.net%252fimage%252f2015-11%252f51747018_02_d-1024x768_f-0_c-512x384.jpg%26w%3D843%26h%3D768&h=52d44b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後網友也查出了這家廠商總部設在台灣彰化，專營汽車的避震器跟避震器控制系統，經銷通路遍佈美國、歐洲、日本、中東等各個國家，這次藉由展覽又再度將台灣精神發揚光大，真的算是台灣之光啊！"},{"pid":"73dd65c75b10ca18c93edac5b3b66e469a1ac567","tid":60140,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:27:24.000Z","msg":"除咗香港，諗唔到有咩大國會理支那呢啲on9抗議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f00e14c1aee36ad6e4ba0fe8a86056e270d99a7","tid":60140,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T08:31:04.000Z","msg":"「那個國家攤位的人跟蒼蠅一樣嗡嗡叫吵死了，我們吃飯就別提這種會讓人食慾不振的事了！」<br />\n<br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9be5dbd4336ecff6fe2f30349d7dfa2d0b8a49","tid":60140,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:00:58.000Z","msg":"收皮啦支那, 又粗暴干涉別國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d89e53ba83feb4aace07b7490a4dabdba26acf1","tid":60140,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f082e90eb20cf4d9ac2012016a562c4b9382de6","tid":60140,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:50:49.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/1500450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F1500450&d=jYQxgPNCiBBMWRoR2vEy0EsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=13f0b942\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F1500450&h=0158c948\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/1500450</a>"},{"pid":"ae6efc0bdc41a2b8805a4051b6969bb07f299497","tid":60140,"uid":63631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:07:23.000Z","msg":"Taiwan number 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514f1ab7d20331bec3d9220100ec49fa85766821","tid":60140,"uid":9778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"又係台仔打飛機文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669d81725d67fae5dc9f06a09507fcb85df3ee7e","tid":60140,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:13:10.000Z","msg":"最後網友也查出了這家廠商總部設在台灣彰化，專營汽車的避震器跟避震器控制系統，經銷通路遍佈美國、歐洲、日本、中東等各個國家，這次藉由展覽又再度將台灣精神發揚光大，真的算是台灣之光啊！<br />\n<br />\n咁又可以成地精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93d36952743609412ff0006038efe0e127c8c9d","tid":60140,"uid":36111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:19:53.000Z","msg":"明明係中華民國國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621e3025ddaef81bc71a14fbd3f264b3d8d7b5e7","tid":60140,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T23:04:28.000Z","msg":"台狗做咩對中華民國國旗扯旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e53b06e8834b7253378628a784aa6eb795e3ce3","tid":60140,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T23:10:14.000Z","msg":"閱"}]}